OL,4,Cand a future defined by AI
OL,6,FFacebook remains one of the most
OL,7,Finfluential pieces of technology in
OL,8,Fthe world, an expert has said, despite
OL,9,Frecent scandals, pressure from rivals
OL,10,Fand other issues it faces as it marks
OL,11,Fits 20th anniversary.
OL,13,FFounded by a group including chief
OL,14,Fexecutive Mark Zuckerberg in a Harvard
OL,15,Fdormitory in 2004, it has grown to
OL,16,Fbecome one of the largest technology
OL,17,Fcompanies in the world as Meta ` the
OL,18,Fparent firm of Facebook and its
OL,19,Fsibling apps Messenger, WhatsApp and
OL,20,FInstagram.
