OL,6,FOver its 20-year existence, Facebook
OL,7,Fhas helped usher in the era of social
OL,8,Fmedia as a communication space,
OL,9,Fcontent creation outlet and news
OL,10,Fsource, but also been at the heart of
OL,11,Fmajor scandals, including the
OL,12,FCambridge Analytica data breach, as
OL,13,Fwell as increased concerns about the
OL,14,Fimpact of the internet, and
OL,15,Fspecifically social media, on health
OL,16,Fand wellbeing, the mental health of
OL,17,Fyounger users, and on the very
OL,18,Ffoundations of democracy.
