OL,6,FEven that good news came as the
OL,7,Fcompany and Zuckerberg was in the
OL,8,Fspotlight for the site's negative
OL,9,Fimpact ` a bruising appearance for the
OL,10,Fbillionaire before the US Congress saw
OL,11,Fhim face, and apologise to, families
OL,12,Fof children who died after being
OL,13,Faffected by online harms while
OL,14,FFacebook was labelled a product
OL,15,F"that's killing people" by one
OL,16,Fsenator, and tech platforms were
OL,17,Faccused of failing to protect young
OL,18,Fpeople.
