OL,6,FAmid the scandals, social media expert
OL,7,FDrew Benvie says it can be easy to
OL,8,Fforget how transformative Facebook has
OL,9,Fbeen for the modern world.
OL,11,F"Mark Zuckerberg, with his hunger for
OL,12,Fsuccess, fame, transformation and
OL,13,Fdemocratisation of everything, really
OL,14,Fdid usher in a totally new era of
OL,15,Finformation and entertainment," he
OL,16,Ftold the PA news agency.
OL,26,@sD@AOUwD@_O]
