OL,4,Cand a future defined by AI
OL,6,F"We shouldn't forget just how
OL,7,Finfluential Facebook is now, through
OL,8,Fits parent company Meta and its sister
OL,9,Fcompanies ` Instagram, WhatsApp and
OL,10,Fothers that it absorbed along the way.
OL,12,F"Over three billion monthly users are
OL,13,Fon one of Meta's platforms ` that's
OL,14,Ftwo-thirds of the internet-connected
OL,15,Fworld ` and whether it's messaging,
OL,16,Fscrolling stories, local community
OL,17,Fgroups, elections, shopping,
OL,18,Fentertainment or keeping in touch,
OL,19,Fit's absolutely changed the world."
