OL,6,FDespite the apparent threats to the
OL,7,Fplatform from regulators and indeed
OL,8,Frival platforms, Mr Benvie believes
OL,9,Fthe social network is not going
OL,10,Fanywhere any time soon.
OL,12,F"I think we've got another 20 years
OL,13,Fahead of us. I think what Zuckerberg
OL,14,Fhas done and what he plans to do,
OL,15,Flargely down to investments in
OL,16,Fmessaging, entertainment, and then the
OL,17,Fnewest move, which is building AI that
OL,18,Fwill power the future of Meta,
OL,19,FFacebook, WhatsApp and Instagram.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
