OL,6,F"I think there's a lot of life in the
OL,7,Fold dog yet," he said, noting that how
OL,8,Fthe company responds to the changing
OL,9,Fregulatory landscape around will shape
OL,10,Fits future.
OL,12,F"The regulation that is coming, I
OL,13,Fthink that's going to be a big part of
OL,14,FFacebook's future too, because nobody
OL,15,Fwants to be made to feel unhappy, ill
OL,16,For for harm to be caused because of
OL,17,Fthe ease and the speed at which
OL,18,Finformation travels on social media.
