OL,4,Cand a future defined by AI
OL,6,F"For that, social networks have a lot
OL,7,Fto answer for and I think there's a
OL,8,Flot of responsibility that's going to
OL,9,Fbe laid on their shoulders in the
OL,10,Ffuture as well, largely on the biggest
OL,11,Fapps, such as Facebook and its family
OL,12,Fof apps.
OL,14,F"The rough direction of travel is that
OL,15,Fthe social networks are clamping down
OL,16,F(on harmful content) as much as they
OL,17,Fcan."
