OL,6,FHe added that artificial intelligence
OL,7,F(AI) will be another key aspect of the
OL,8,Fplatform's future ` an area Meta has
OL,9,Falready begun investing in and last
OL,10,Fyear announced its first chatbots
OL,11,Fbuilt using its own Llarma large
OL,12,Flanguage model.
OL,14,FMr Benvie said it will not be this
OL,15,Fapplication of AI, but how Meta uses
OL,16,Fit more broadly that could define its
OL,17,Fnext two decades.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G10/18
