OL,6,F"Increasingly that (moderation) is the
OL,7,Fjob of technology to do and not human
OL,8,Fmoderators, so that's where AI, I
OL,9,Fthink, will play a big part in Meta's
OL,10,Ffuture," he said.
OL,12,F"In the future, AI will help detect
OL,13,Fcontent that maybe shouldn't be there
OL,14,Fand it will help remove it quicker,
OL,15,Fand it will do other fantastic things
OL,16,Ffor social media. It will give users
OL,17,Ftools and technologies they've not had
OL,18,Fbefore.
