OL,6,F"I think AI will do a lot for keeping
OL,7,Fpeople safer online and it will also
OL,8,Fimprove people's experiences of social
OL,9,Fmedia too, if done in the right way.
OL,10,FSo, I think that is something to look
OL,11,Fforward to.
OL,13,F"AI is such a huge space to watch and
OL,14,Fit isn't just a social media-related
OL,15,Ftopic either, it's in all lines of
OL,16,Fwork, so Meta could expand way beyond
OL,17,Fsocial media if it gets the AI right,
OL,18,Fso it's definitely one to watch."
