OL,6,FHowever, one area of innovation Mr
OL,7,FBenvie said has so far been "a bit of
OL,8,Fa mistake" has been the firm's
OL,9,Finvestment in the metaverse.
OL,11,FThe social media expert said he
OL,12,Fbelieved the company had been "just
OL,13,Ftoo quick to innovate" and would have
OL,14,Fbeen better off waiting for interest
OL,15,Fin the technology to grow more.
