OL,6,FZuckerberg pledged billions of dollars
OL,7,Fand rebranded the company in order to
OL,8,Flaunch his metaverse project, a 3D
OL,9,Fmixed reality space he said he
OL,10,Fbelieves is the future of the
OL,11,Finternet, but as yet does not exist as
OL,12,Fany one, tangible space or platform.
OL,14,FDespite his very hands-on approach
OL,15,Faround the metaverse, Mr Benvie said
OL,16,Fhe could see Zuckerberg following the
OL,17,Fexample of other high-profile tech
OL,18,Ffounders and stepping back from day-to-
OL,19,Fday management at some point.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G14/18
