OL,6,F"Maybe we'll see Mark Zuckerberg take
OL,7,Fa bit of a step back, a bit like we've
OL,8,Fseen from founders of other innovative
OL,9,Ftechnologies in the social media space
OL,10,F` I'm thinking Larry Page and Sergey
OL,11,FBrin from Google, Bill Gates at
OL,12,FMicrosoft ` they still have an
OL,13,Finfluence ` Mark Zuckerberg would
OL,14,Fprobably still have a heavy influence,
OL,15,Fbut it'll reach a point where we see
OL,16,Fhis other interests take over," he
OL,17,Fsaid.
